Package: ForestKDE
Title: Kernel Density Estimation with Random Forests
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "McCoy",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "david_mccoy@berkeley.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5515-6307"))
Description: Implements a methodology that combines random forests and kernel
    density estimation for improved prediction performance. The package provides
    a cross-validated model selection method to find the best parameters for
    the random forest and kernel functions.
